title: Jungle ez is pretty strong
body:
Discuss

http://matchhistory.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/#match-details/NA1/1642390510/203960328

http://matchhistory.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/#match-details/NA1/1642216995/203960328?tab=overview

You can run through the jungle with almost no dmg. Your team doesn't need to leash.

Start rock golems so you get the stun proc while kiting. Your q counts as a hit so you proc the stun often allowing for no resetting.

High range+mobility makes for easy ganks.

Rush devourers on skirmisher to smite enemys for slow+extra true dmg
Build 

Jungle item>Sheen/static shyv> other >lucid boots> Tf/IBG>Mana reaver>ie or some last item according to comp
